		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />gzclose takes a gzFile as a parameter, is fp a gzFile or a gzFile*? (it seems you should be using a gzFile)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
